                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def2-481-18410104 t18410104-481-punishment-69"></join>Confined Three Months</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Baron Rolfe</hi>.</p>
